  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Striking with both of your weapons simultaneously, you can use them to deliver devastating wounds.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />Dex 17, Double Slice, Improved Two-Weapon Fighting, Two-Weapon Fighting, base attack bonus +11.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />If you hit an opponent with both your primary hand and your off-hand weapon, you deal an additional 1d10 points of damage plus 1-1/2 times your Strength modifier. You can only deal this additional damage once each round.<br /><br /><strong>Combat Trick</strong><br />You can spend 5 stamina points to use this feat's benefit a second time in a single round.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong>: create the \"Two-Weapon Rend\" Damage conditional modifier as Non-critical Damge Bonus Formula. Formula is \"1d10 + floor(1.5*@abilities.str.mod)\"</p>",
